sql:
SELECT AVG(p.material_cost) AS average_material_cost
FROM prices p
INNER JOIN recipes r ON p.item_id = r.item_id;

external_knowledge:
- 'Top 5' refers to the items with the highest campaign usage count and the shortest average crafting time; 
- 'Frequently used items' are those that appear in the most campaigns; 
- 'Shortest crafting times' refer to the average time required to craft each item.
